# LLM Call Rules

Every LLM call MUST:

- Return structured JSON
- Have explicit schema validation
- Never control transitions directly
- Never access hidden ground truth unless explicitly allowed

LLMs are language generators, not decision engines.

All decisions must be validated by Python logic.